Project  𝄀
  ->  Index Table Scan on spatial_idx_path.idx_g  𝄀
        Filter Cond: st_intersects(__mo_index_idx_col, 'POINT(1 1)')
explain select payload from spatial_idx_path where st_intersects(g, st_geomfromtext('POINT(1 1)'));
➤ TP QUERY PLAN[12,0,0]  𝄀
Project  𝄀
  ->  Join  𝄀
        Join Type: INDEX  𝄀
        Join Cond: (spatial_idx_path.id = __mo_index_pri_col)  𝄀
        Runtime Filter Build: #[-1,0]  𝄀
        ->  Table Scan on func_geometry_spatial_index.spatial_idx_path [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
              Filter Cond: st_intersects(spatial_idx_path.g, 'POINT(1 1)')  𝄀
              Runtime Filter Probe: spatial_idx_path.id  𝄀
        ->  Index Table Scan on spatial_idx_path.idx_g [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
              Filter Cond: st_intersects(__mo_index_idx_col, 'POINT(1 1)')
